                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>\n                <addressee>Revd I. Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Your<lb/> letters of the <date>5<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi></date> Ins\n                came<lb/> duly to hand, since which<lb/> a box containing<lb/> 2 of the New\n                Edition<lb/> of the 40 Bible with the<lb/> parcels pr <persName>Cohen</persName>,<lb/>\n                <persName>Jacobs</persName>, <persName>Mois</persName> &amp;\n                        <persName>Bradl<add>?</add></persName><lb/> have been safely landed<lb/>\n                &amp; all the parcels deli<lb/>vered &amp; forwarded as<lb/> directed.</p>\n            <p>You ask for the docu<lb/>ments in relation to the<lb/> debate that took place<lb/>\n                between <persName>Dr Raphall</persName><lb/>\n                <persName>PB</persName> &amp; <persName>Wise</persName>, <persName>Mr.\n                    Levin</persName><lb/> took down the debate<lb/> at the occasion &amp;\n                trans<lb/>mitted them to <persName>Dr. R</persName></p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3qr4p998/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
